<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-sales-books-purchase-books.md" sourcestartlinenumber="116">Lines</td>
<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-sales-books-purchase-books.md" sourcestartlinenumber="116">Open the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-sales-books-purchase-books.md" sourcestartlinenumber="116">Purchase book lines</strong> page, where you can verify the details of the purchase book lines.</td>
</tr>
<tr sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-sales-books-purchase-books.md" sourcestartlinenumber="117">
<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-sales-books-purchase-books.md" sourcestartlinenumber="117">Totals</td>
<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-sales-books-purchase-books.md" sourcestartlinenumber="117">Open the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-sales-books-purchase-books.md" sourcestartlinenumber="117">Totals</strong> dialog box, where you can review total VAT base and VAT amounts for the purchase book.</td>
</tr>
<tr sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-sales-books-purchase-books.md" sourcestartlinenumber="118">
<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-sales-books-purchase-books.md" sourcestartlinenumber="118">Print &gt; Purchase book</td>
<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-sales-books-purchase-books.md" sourcestartlinenumber="118">Print the purchase book report.</td>
</tr>
<tr sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-sales-books-purchase-books.md" sourcestartlinenumber="119">
